apm.name: Abstract Frame Latch
apm.description: Frame latch provides a way to create a value and attach a model that transitions between waiting and updated process steps whenever the value is written. This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

updated.description: The value managed by the frame latch has been written.

waiting.description: Frame latch value has not changed since last signalled update.

filterDescriptor.operationDescription: Writes the value made observable by frame latch APM instance.

This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

updated.description: The value managed by the frame latch has been written.

waiting.description: Frame latch value has not changed since last signalled update.

filterDescriptor.operationDescription: Writes the value made observable by frame latch APM instance.

artifact.name: Abstract Frame Latch
artifact.description: Frame latch provides a way to create a value and attach a model that transitions between waiting and updated process steps whenever the value is written. This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

updated.description: The value managed by the frame latch has been written.

waiting.description: Frame latch value has not changed since last signalled update.

filterDescriptor.operationDescription: Writes the value made observable by frame latch APM instance.
